data.description: Dreamy Craftsman Oasis Awaits! Nestled perfectly at the end of a quiet cul-de-sac, discover this stunning custom Craftsman charmer with no HOA strings attached! First, lets talk finances. Tap into the golden opportunity of an assumable loan at an unbelievable 2.75 interest rate. Current balance holder is on standby to bridge the gap at the best rate you qualify for on the remaining balance. Now, lets dive into the magic within: Age is just a number, but at just over 3 years young, she's practically sparkling new and impeccably maintained. Embrace the outdoors with nearly 1.5 acres of walkable land, complete with a serene creek at its tail. Low maintenance concrete siding paired elegantly with stone accents, the inviting covered front porch is an inviting place for morning birds and coffee, and that dreamy rear covered patio complete with roaring firepit sits with an elevated view of the private back yard. Step inside to a world of sophisticated updates: ambient light fixtures, fans, a captivating stone fireplace, and 9 ft ceilings. Chefs paradise alert: A kitchen that boasts granite counters, sleek stainless appliances, and that showstopper – a grand custom island with intricate wood details that promises not just function, but form too. Its loaded with extra storage yet adds seating for 6! Its got that that open floorplan you've been looking for. Easy, breezy transitions from the kitchen to the family room ensure you never miss a word of conversation on those nights of entertaining! The regal owners suite on the main floor is the retreat you've been waiting for: vaulted ceilings, a chic modern fan, and a sumptuous bath, with separate tub and shower, that promises relaxation. We have just scratched the surface! The laundry room just received custom cabinets making it a mudroom too by incorporating a seating spot, storage shelves and a folding surface. The upper floor offers 3 more bedrooms, one of which is so spacious the current owners have it outfitted with sectional couch and use it for a theater room. This floor also has the third luxe bath, like all the baths, features custom butcher block tops with vessel sinks and modern fixtures. The main hall has a birds-eye view of the family sanctuary below. Don't just dream it, live it! Secure your exclusive showing NOW and step into the lifestyle you deserve. Your dream home at Rocky’s Bluff is waiting – will you answer the call?
